OL,3,CAnimal Rescue says rising vets bills
OL,4,Care challenging their operation
OL,6,FAn animal rescue centre in Basingstoke
OL,7,Fsays rising vets bills and the cost of
OL,8,Fliving are making it difficult to keep
OL,9,Fgoing.
OL,11,FHelping Dogs and Cats Rescue fosters,
OL,12,Fre-homes and cares for hundreds of
OL,13,Fanimals each year.
OL,15,FSome are strays and others are handed
OL,16,Fin by the public or the vet.
OL,18,FAll animals are medically assessed and
OL,19,Fthe rescue team works with them on any
OL,20,Fbehavioural issues.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
