OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777543610
OL,3,CAnimal Rescue says rising vets bills
OL,4,Care challenging their operation
OL,6,FThey're currently supporting around 50
OL,7,Fanimals - mainly cats - and are
OL,8,Foperating at capacity. They fear
OL,9,Fincreasing costs will mean turning
OL,10,Fanimals away.
OL,12,FKirsty Wrightson set up the rescue
OL,13,Feight years ago.
OL,15,FIt relies on public donations and
OL,16,Ffundraising but she says vets bills
OL,17,Fare the biggest challenge - often
OL,18,Fthree to five thousand pounds each
OL,19,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777543610
OL,3,CAnimal Rescue says rising vets bills
OL,4,Care challenging their operation
OL,6,FKirsty said: "Already this week we've
OL,7,Ftaken in six cats.
OL,9,F"And with each of those cats you've
OL,10,Fgot to neuter them, you've got to
OL,11,Fvaccinate them. And there just isn't
OL,12,Fenough money to go around for the vet
OL,13,Fbills.
OL,15,F"So we are struggling on a day to day
OL,16,Fbasis, and the money side of it,
OL,17,Funfortunately, stops us from being
OL,18,Fable to help others, which is really
OL,19,Fsad but money makes the world go
OL,20,Fround, unfortunately."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
