CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777543610
OL,3,CAnimal Rescue says rising vets bills
OL,4,Care challenging their operation
OL,6,FHelping Cats and Dogs Rescue is a
OL,7,Fcommunity interest company. They also
OL,8,Foperate a grooming service and animal
OL,9,Ffood bank to help people keep their
OL,10,Fpets at home.
OL,12,FThey are currently helping over 280
OL,13,Fpeople in the Basingstoke and Tadley
OL,14,FArea.
OL,16,FKirsty said: "We operate through
OL,17,Fdonations from the public.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777543610
OL,3,CAnimal Rescue says rising vets bills
OL,4,Care challenging their operation
OL,6,F"We started that up probably about
OL,7,Ffive years ago. And our aim is to keep
OL,8,Floved animals, where people are
OL,9,Fstruggling with the cost of living, in
OL,10,Ftheir homes, so people can come in and
OL,11,Fwe can help support them with that."
OL,13,FMost of the animals they support live
OL,14,Fwith foster carers until new homes can
OL,15,Fbe found. The rescue needs more
OL,16,Ffostering volunteers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
