PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777543610
OL,3,CAnimal Rescue says rising vets bills
OL,4,Care challenging their operation
OL,6,FAmy Chapman, Assistant Manager and a
OL,7,Ffosterer said: "Fostering works where
OL,8,Fyou open your home up to animals, all
OL,9,Fdifferent shapes and sizes and needs,
OL,10,Fand you bring them in.
OL,12,F"You show them comfort, love, family.
OL,13,FAnd then the best thing is finding
OL,14,Ftheir forever home."
OL,16,FHelping Dogs and Cats Rescue
OL,17,Fvolunteers say although they are
OL,18,Fstruggling with costs, demand for
OL,19,Ftheir services is growing. They're
OL,20,Fhoping to expand to be able to take on
OL,21,Fmore animals in need in the future.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
